title: Street Politicians: How To Invest In Yourself Pt 2
itunes:title: Street Politicians: How To Invest In Yourself Pt 2
description:
The Black Effect Presents... Street Politicians.

This week Tamika and Mysonne are continuing their work on obtaining knowledge on sustaining financial ability within our community, with special guest 19 Keys. In this episode 19 Keys spoke on how he got involved in NFT's and building financial literacy for his community, and uplifting his people. Next they speak with the owner of Brooklyn Chop House, Robert ”Don Pooh” Cummins, who spoke to them about his business, understanding how to network and combining NFT's with his business.
